data.description: Welcome to this charming and well-maintained home featuring three spacious bedrooms and two full bathrooms. As you enter, you’re greeted by a warm and inviting living room, highlighted by abundant natural light. The heart of the home is the bright and airy kitchen, boasting modern appliances, ample cabinet space, and subway tile backsplash, creating the perfect environment for culinary exploration. It flows seamlessly into the dining area, making it ideal for gatherings. The outdoor area, adorned with a covered patio and mature landscaping, offers a private oasis for outdoor dining and entertainment. In addition, this house is equipped with solar panels to help you save hundreds of dollars on your electrical bill! This home’s additional features include a long driveway and a two-car garage, Situated in a serene neighborhood, it provides easy access to local amenities and is a delightful place to call home. Don’t miss out on the opportunity to own this inviting residence, where every detail contributes to creating a delightful living experience.
